Class RowCalcReducer

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.hadoop.mapreduce.Reducer<org.apache.hadoop.io.IntWritable,BytesArrayWritable,org.apache.hadoop.io.LongWritable,org.apache.hadoop.io.Text>
      • org.enquery.encryptedquery.responder.wideskies.mapreduce.RowCalcReducer

  • public class RowCalcReducer
extends org.apache.hadoop.mapreduce.Reducer<org.apache.hadoop.io.IntWritable,BytesArrayWritable,org.apache.hadoop.io.LongWritable,org.apache.hadoop.io.Text>
    Reducer class to calculate the encrypted rows of the encrypted query

    For each row (as indicated by key = hash(selector)), iterates over each dataElement and calculates the column values.

    Emits <colNum, colVal>
